"Features: 

  * 10 Single Player Missions 

  * Control a squad of rangers - orders include Go, Engage, Cease Fire 
    and Hold Position. 

  * Authentic vehicles - HMMVVS and Blackhawks. 

  * 9 Real world weapons: M9 Beretta, CAR-15, M16 with M103 grenade 
    launcher, MG249 SAW, M40A1 Sniper Rifle, Frag Grenade, Shotgun, 
    and LAW. 

  * Night Vision Goggles 

  * Get air support from Little Birds and Blackhawks. 

  * In game mission map with waypoints to help players complete mission 
    objectives."
